name: Reinterpretation of Dali's "The Burning Giraffe" #002!
description: "The Burning Giraffe" was hugely influenced by the emergence of psychoanalysis. Drawers in the human body could open a new possibility of exploration of the human mind. In this reinterpretation, I opt to change the original art color and components [can someone find the penis?! hahaha]
